HEAT

HEAT

^RHeat^n is attention from the authorities. When you have heat, your prompt shows a small red meter like ^R[▉▉▉ m:ss]^n.
- The blocks indicate rough heat tier (1–3).
- The timer shows time to the next drop in heat.
- The HUD only appears while you have heat and disappears at 0.

^yHow do I get heat?^n Crimes, suspicious activity, or getting caught.

^yHow do I lower it?^n Lay low, avoid crowds, stop causing trouble, and give it time to decay.

^WSee also:^n POLICEPROC, STEAL, PICKPOCKET, CASE
